{"id":"ZPRAC_CDS_ASSOCIATION","title":"demand join relationship","phase":3,"phaseName":"Joins & Associations","category":"Joins & Associations","subcategory":"Associations","language":"abap","description":"CDS Association — lazy/on-demand join relationship. Key topics: Association is a DECLARED relationship — NOT executed as a join. Data is fetched lazily (on demand) when the association is accessed. Cardinality: [1] → exactly one, [0..1] → zero or one, [*] → many.","sections":[{"title":"Key Learning Points","description":"<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Association is a DECLARED relationship — NOT executed as a join</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Data is fetched lazily (on demand) when the association is accessed</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Cardinality: [1] → exactly one, [0..1] → zero or one, [*] → many</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>To expose the association publicly, include it in the SELECT list</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Consumption via path expression: _Assoc._Customer.FirstName</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Associations can be accessed in WHERE clause - implicit join</span></div></div>"},{"title":"Concept Diagram","description":"<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-g\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#22C55E\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-y\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#EAB308\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Association vs Composition in CDS</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ ASSOCIATION SIDE ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"25\" y=\"70\" width=\"465\" height=\"350\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <rect x=\"25\" y=\"70\" width=\"465\" height=\"36\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#22C55E\"/>\n  <rect x=\"25\" y=\"90\" width=\"465\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#22C55E\"/>\n  <text x=\"45\" y=\"94\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Association (read-only link)</text>\n\n  <!-- CDS syntax -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"118\" width=\"435\" height=\"95\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"138\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">define view ZV_Travel</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  as select from /dmo/travel</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"172\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#22C55E\">  association [0..1] to /dmo/agency</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"189\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#22C55E\">    as _Agency on $projection.AgencyId = _Agency.agency_id</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"206\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">{ key travel_id, agency_id, _Agency.name }</text>\n\n  <!-- Visual model -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"228\" width=\"180\" height=\"55\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#DCFCE7\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"160\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#15803D\">Travel (Root)</text>\n  <text x=\"160\" y=\"268\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#166534\">Own identity &amp; persistence</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"250\" y1=\"255\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"255\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr-g)\"/>\n  <text x=\"270\" y=\"248\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#22C55E\">reads</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"295\" y=\"228\" width=\"180\" height=\"55\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"385\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#15803D\">Agency (Target)</text>\n  <text x=\"385\" y=\"268\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#166534\">Exists independently</text>\n\n  <!-- Cardinality -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"300\" width=\"405\" height=\"45\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"272\" y=\"320\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Cardinality: [0..1] Zero or one · [1] Exactly one · [*] Many</text>\n  <text x=\"272\" y=\"338\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Path expression: $projection.AssocName.field → automatic JOIN</text>\n\n  <!-- Properties box -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"358\" width=\"435\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"376\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">✅ <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">Read-only</tspan> — use in SELECT or path expression</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"394\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">✅ <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">Target is independent</tspan> — can exist without the source</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"400\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">✅ Lazy-loaded — no JOIN unless path expression is used</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ COMPOSITION SIDE ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"70\" width=\"465\" height=\"350\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"70\" width=\"465\" height=\"36\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\"/>\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"90\" width=\"465\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#EAB308\"/>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"94\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Composition (parent-child)</text>\n\n  <!-- CDS syntax -->\n  <rect x=\"525\" y=\"118\" width=\"435\" height=\"95\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"138\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">define root view entity ZV_TravelRoot</text>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  as select from /dmo/travel</text>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"172\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\">  composition [0..*] of /dmo/booking</text>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"189\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\">    as _Booking on $projection.TravelId = _Booking.travel_id</text>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"206\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">{ key travel_id, _Booking.* }</text>\n\n  <!-- Visual model -->\n  <rect x=\"545\" y=\"228\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEF9C3\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"745\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A16207\">Travel (Root Entity)</text>\n  <text x=\"745\" y=\"268\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#854D0E\">Owns children — cannot exist without root</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"565\" y=\"280\" width=\"360\" height=\"38\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#FFFBEB\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,2\"/>\n  <text x=\"745\" y=\"298\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A16207\">Booking (Child)</text>\n  <text x=\"745\" y=\"314\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#854D0E\">Root UUID is part of child key</text>\n\n  <!-- Cardinality -->\n  <rect x=\"525\" y=\"340\" width=\"435\" height=\"32\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"742\" y=\"358\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Cardinality: [0..*] Zero or many · [0..1] Zero or one · [1..*] At least one</text>\n\n  <!-- Properties box -->\n  <rect x=\"525\" y=\"378\" width=\"435\" height=\"30\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"396\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">✅ <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">Parent-child</tspan> — child has dependent lifecycle</text>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"402\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">✅ Child <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">cannot exist without parent</tspan> (root UUID in key)</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ COMPARISON TABLE ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"25\" y=\"435\" width=\"950\" height=\"300\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"460\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Association vs Composition — Comparison Table</text>\n  <line x1=\"45\" y1=\"468\" x2=\"955\" y2=\"468\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"45\" y=\"475\" width=\"910\" height=\"24\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"492\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Aspect</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"492\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Association</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"492\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Composition</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"45\" y1=\"499\" x2=\"955\" y2=\"499\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"522\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Relationship</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"522\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#22C55E\">Read-only reference</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"522\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\">Parent-child (whole-part)</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Target Lifecycle</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Independent (can exist alone)</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Dependent (dies with parent)</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"572\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Cardinality</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"572\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">[0..1], [1], [*]</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"572\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">[0..*], [0..1], [1..*]</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"597\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Key Inheritance</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"597\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">No (separate keys)</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"597\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Root UUID in child key</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"622\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Loading</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"622\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Lazy (via path expression)</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"622\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Eager (part of parent)</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"647\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Use in SELECT</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"647\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Path expression: _Assoc.field</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"647\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Cannot be selected directly</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"672\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">RAP Behavior</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"672\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Read-only (no create/update)</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"672\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Create/update/delete via parent</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"697\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Example</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"697\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Travel → Agency (lookup)</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"697\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Travel → Booking (items)</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"45\" y1=\"705\" x2=\"955\" y2=\"705\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"722\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Associations = loose coupling · Compositions = tight coupling with lifecycle management</text>\n</svg></div>"},{"title":"CDS Source Code","language":"abap","codeBlock":"@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_ASSOC'\n@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true\n@AbapCatalog.preserveKey: true\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\n@EndUserText.label: 'Practice CDS - Association (lazy join) to Customer'\ndefine view ZPRAC_CDS_ASSOCIATION\n  as select from /DMO/I_Booking_D as _Booking\n\n  /*\n   * Association definition:\n   *   [1] = cardinality (exactly one Customer per Booking)\n   *   to /DMO/I_Customer = target CDS view\n   *   as _Customer = alias used for path expressions\n   *   on ... = condition linking source to target\n   *\n   * Default cardinality when not specified: [1]\n   */\n  association [1] to /DMO/I_Customer as _Customer\n    on _Booking.CustomerID = _Customer.CustomerID\n\n{\n  key _Booking.BookingUUID,\n      _Booking.TravelUUID,\n      _Booking.BookingID,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Booking.BookingDate,\n      _Booking.CustomerID,\n      _Booking.AirlineID,\n      _Booking.ConnectionID,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Booking.FlightDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      _Booking.FlightPrice,\n      _Booking.CurrencyCode,\n      _Booking.BookingStatus,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Booking.LocalLastChangedAt,\n\n  /*\n   * Expose the association publicly so consumers can traverse it:\n   *   Include _Customer in the field list\n   *   Consumers can now write: _Customer.FirstName (path expression)\n   */\n      _Customer\n}"}],"content":"<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_ASSOCIATION-key-learning-points\">Key Learning Points</h2>\n<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Association is a DECLARED relationship — NOT executed as a join</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Data is fetched lazily (on demand) when the association is accessed</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Cardinality: [1] → exactly one, [0..1] → zero or one, [*] → many</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>To expose the association publicly, include it in the SELECT list</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Consumption via path expression: _Assoc._Customer.FirstName</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Associations can be accessed in WHERE clause - implicit join</span></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_ASSOCIATION-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-g\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#22C55E\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-y\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#EAB308\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Association vs Composition in CDS</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ ASSOCIATION SIDE ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"25\" y=\"70\" width=\"465\" height=\"350\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <rect x=\"25\" y=\"70\" width=\"465\" height=\"36\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#22C55E\"/>\n  <rect x=\"25\" y=\"90\" width=\"465\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#22C55E\"/>\n  <text x=\"45\" y=\"94\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Association (read-only link)</text>\n\n  <!-- CDS syntax -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"118\" width=\"435\" height=\"95\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"138\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">define view ZV_Travel</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  as select from /dmo/travel</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"172\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#22C55E\">  association [0..1] to /dmo/agency</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"189\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#22C55E\">    as _Agency on $projection.AgencyId = _Agency.agency_id</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"206\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">{ key travel_id, agency_id, _Agency.name }</text>\n\n  <!-- Visual model -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"228\" width=\"180\" height=\"55\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#DCFCE7\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"160\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#15803D\">Travel (Root)</text>\n  <text x=\"160\" y=\"268\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#166534\">Own identity &amp; persistence</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"250\" y1=\"255\" x2=\"290\" y2=\"255\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr-g)\"/>\n  <text x=\"270\" y=\"248\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#22C55E\">reads</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"295\" y=\"228\" width=\"180\" height=\"55\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"385\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#15803D\">Agency (Target)</text>\n  <text x=\"385\" y=\"268\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#166534\">Exists independently</text>\n\n  <!-- Cardinality -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"300\" width=\"405\" height=\"45\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"272\" y=\"320\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Cardinality: [0..1] Zero or one · [1] Exactly one · [*] Many</text>\n  <text x=\"272\" y=\"338\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Path expression: $projection.AssocName.field → automatic JOIN</text>\n\n  <!-- Properties box -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"358\" width=\"435\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"376\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">✅ <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">Read-only</tspan> — use in SELECT or path expression</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"394\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">✅ <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">Target is independent</tspan> — can exist without the source</text>\n  <text x=\"55\" y=\"400\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">✅ Lazy-loaded — no JOIN unless path expression is used</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ COMPOSITION SIDE ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"70\" width=\"465\" height=\"350\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"70\" width=\"465\" height=\"36\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\"/>\n  <rect x=\"510\" y=\"90\" width=\"465\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#EAB308\"/>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"94\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Composition (parent-child)</text>\n\n  <!-- CDS syntax -->\n  <rect x=\"525\" y=\"118\" width=\"435\" height=\"95\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"138\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">define root view entity ZV_TravelRoot</text>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">  as select from /dmo/travel</text>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"172\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\">  composition [0..*] of /dmo/booking</text>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"189\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\">    as _Booking on $projection.TravelId = _Booking.travel_id</text>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"206\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">{ key travel_id, _Booking.* }</text>\n\n  <!-- Visual model -->\n  <rect x=\"545\" y=\"228\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEF9C3\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"745\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A16207\">Travel (Root Entity)</text>\n  <text x=\"745\" y=\"268\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#854D0E\">Owns children — cannot exist without root</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"565\" y=\"280\" width=\"360\" height=\"38\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#FFFBEB\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,2\"/>\n  <text x=\"745\" y=\"298\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A16207\">Booking (Child)</text>\n  <text x=\"745\" y=\"314\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#854D0E\">Root UUID is part of child key</text>\n\n  <!-- Cardinality -->\n  <rect x=\"525\" y=\"340\" width=\"435\" height=\"32\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"742\" y=\"358\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Cardinality: [0..*] Zero or many · [0..1] Zero or one · [1..*] At least one</text>\n\n  <!-- Properties box -->\n  <rect x=\"525\" y=\"378\" width=\"435\" height=\"30\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"396\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">✅ <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">Parent-child</tspan> — child has dependent lifecycle</text>\n  <text x=\"540\" y=\"402\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">✅ Child <tspan font-weight=\"bold\">cannot exist without parent</tspan> (root UUID in key)</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ COMPARISON TABLE ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"25\" y=\"435\" width=\"950\" height=\"300\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"460\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Association vs Composition — Comparison Table</text>\n  <line x1=\"45\" y1=\"468\" x2=\"955\" y2=\"468\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <rect x=\"45\" y=\"475\" width=\"910\" height=\"24\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"492\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Aspect</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"492\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Association</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"492\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Composition</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"45\" y1=\"499\" x2=\"955\" y2=\"499\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"522\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Relationship</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"522\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#22C55E\">Read-only reference</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"522\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#EAB308\">Parent-child (whole-part)</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Target Lifecycle</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Independent (can exist alone)</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"547\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Dependent (dies with parent)</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"572\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Cardinality</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"572\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">[0..1], [1], [*]</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"572\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">[0..*], [0..1], [1..*]</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"597\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Key Inheritance</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"597\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">No (separate keys)</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"597\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Root UUID in child key</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"622\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Loading</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"622\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Lazy (via path expression)</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"622\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Eager (part of parent)</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"647\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Use in SELECT</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"647\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Path expression: _Assoc.field</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"647\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Cannot be selected directly</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"672\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">RAP Behavior</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"672\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Read-only (no create/update)</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"672\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Create/update/delete via parent</text>\n\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"697\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Example</text>\n  <text x=\"380\" y=\"697\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Travel → Agency (lookup)</text>\n  <text x=\"650\" y=\"697\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Travel → Booking (items)</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"45\" y1=\"705\" x2=\"955\" y2=\"705\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"722\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748B\">Associations = loose coupling · Compositions = tight coupling with lifecycle management</text>\n</svg></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_ASSOCIATION-cds-source-code\">CDS Source Code</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-abap\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_ASSOC'\n@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true\n@AbapCatalog.preserveKey: true\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\n@EndUserText.label: 'Practice CDS - Association (lazy join) to Customer'\ndefine view ZPRAC_CDS_ASSOCIATION\n  as select from /DMO/I_Booking_D as _Booking\n\n  /*\n   * Association definition:\n   *   [1] = cardinality (exactly one Customer per Booking)\n   *   to /DMO/I_Customer = target CDS view\n   *   as _Customer = alias used for path expressions\n   *   on ... = condition linking source to target\n   *\n   * Default cardinality when not specified: [1]\n   */\n  association [1] to /DMO/I_Customer as _Customer\n    on _Booking.CustomerID = _Customer.CustomerID\n\n{\n  key _Booking.BookingUUID,\n      _Booking.TravelUUID,\n      _Booking.BookingID,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Booking.BookingDate,\n      _Booking.CustomerID,\n      _Booking.AirlineID,\n      _Booking.ConnectionID,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Booking.FlightDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      _Booking.FlightPrice,\n      _Booking.CurrencyCode,\n      _Booking.BookingStatus,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Booking.LocalLastChangedAt,\n\n  /*\n   * Expose the association publicly so consumers can traverse it:\n   *   Include _Customer in the field list\n   *   Consumers can now write: _Customer.FirstName (path expression)\n   */\n      _Customer\n}</code></pre>","tags":["associations"],"details":"<p class=\"mb-2\">ASSOCIATION vs JOIN:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">┌─────────────┬──────────────────────┬───────────────────┐</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Aspect      │ JOIN                 │ Association       │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">├─────────────┼──────────────────────┼───────────────────┤</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Fetch       │ Eager (always runs)  │ Lazy (on-access)  │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ SQL         │ Generated upfront    │ Dynamic SQL       │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Performance │ Good for small sets  │ Good for optional │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Reuse       │ Coupled              │ Decoupled         │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">└─────────────┴──────────────────────┴───────────────────┘</p><p class=\"mb-2\">CONSUMPTION IN ABAP:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">SELECT BookingUUID, _Customer.FirstName, _Customer.LastName</p><p class=\"mb-2\">FROM ZPRAC_CDS_ASSOCIATION</p><p class=\"mb-2\">INTO TABLE @DATA(lt_bookings).</p><p class=\"mb-2\">--> The _Customer association is resolved automatically by the framework</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DIAGRAM: assets/diagrams/assoc-vs-composition.svg</p>","cdsViewName":"ZPRAC_CDS_ASSOCIATION","sqlViewName":"ZPRAC_SQL_ASSOC","topic":"Defining and exposing associations"}